===Adverb===

# From [[where]].  (''Whence did I come?'')
#:This word is unusual in modern usage; the more common phrase would be ''Where did I come from''.  It is more often encountered in older works, or when used poetically.

====Translations====
*Dutch: [[waarvandaan]]
*German: [[woher]]

